Project:-
Fabricated a Fire-Fighter Robot using Arduino UNO Microcontroller and flame sensors.

A Fire-Fighter robot is one that has a small fire extinguisher added to it.
This robot is designed in such a way that it detects the flames of fire & extinguishes it using a spray of water, before the fire could spread out of range & control.

The project aims to help the firefighters men to save their lives each year throughout the world.
